OL,3,CPolice 'joked' in YouTube clip about
OL,4,Crapper's death, claims grieving mum
OL,6,FCarol Campbell recalled the moment she
OL,7,Ffirst saw the unedited video appear on
OL,8,FYouTube.
OL,10,F"We watch a lot of the YouTube videos,
OL,11,Fso it just automatically came up and
OL,12,Fhe (Craig) popped up on the screen.
OL,14,F"And I said isn't that Craig? I saw
OL,15,Fthe guy come up to him and what he did
OL,16,Fto my son. There was no filter it was
OL,17,Fjust raw. It wasn't it wasn't edited
OL,18,For anything."
