OL,6,FIn a statement, police said the video
OL,7,Fwas referred to the police watchdog
OL,8,Fand the Met is investigating officers
OL,9,Ffor misconduct and gross misconduct.
OL,11,FFollowing an Old Bailey retrial,
OL,12,FCourtney Ellis was found guilty of
OL,13,Fmurder and attempted murder and jailed
OL,14,Ffor at least 35 years.
OL,16,FEllis was also convicted of perverting
OL,17,Fthe course of justice alongside
OL,18,FChristopher Kyei who was jailed for
OL,19,Ffour-and-a-half years.
