OL,6,FThe defendants were said to be
OL,7,Fassociated with a gang that operated
OL,8,Fin north-west London.
OL,10,FCraig was not a gang member but
OL,11,Fassociated with members of two rival
OL,12,Fgangs and found himself a target for
OL,13,Fretaliation.
OL,15,FHe often spoke to his mum about
OL,16,Fviolence and his concerns about
OL,17,Fdisputes between rival gangs.
