OL,4,Crapper's death, claims grieving mum
OL,6,FCarol said after the difficult weeks
OL,7,Fof sitting through the court case she
OL,8,Fnow faced the added burden of waiting
OL,9,Ffor the outcome of the police
OL,10,Finvestigation.
OL,12,FShe added: "My son was very important
OL,13,Fto us, to the whole family.
OL,15,F"My son was my life and the way they
OL,16,Ftook my son, it wasn't right. I'm
OL,17,Fliving that every day.
