OL,6,F"We just finished the court case, so
OL,7,FI'm still going through it and I've
OL,8,Fstill got to go through this in this
OL,9,Fsituation with the police as well.
OL,11,F"So it's hard. It's very hard. The
OL,12,Fknock on effect that it's had on my
OL,13,Fhealth is very hard.
