OL,6,FCarol spoke of how her son loved music
OL,7,Ffirst as a rapper before turning to
OL,8,FR&B and wanted to be a talent scout.
OL,10,FShe added: "We want to enjoy what life
OL,11,Fwe had with him, not thinking about
OL,12,Fthe sorrow of what happened to him.
OL,14,F"And we've got all this going on.
OL,16,F"That's what just making me more
OL,17,Ffocused on what happened to him than
OL,18,Fon the good times that we had with
OL,19,Fhim."
